data.title: Off to Havana I Go
data.meta_description: A La Habana me voy (English language Off to Havana I Go) is a 1951 musical Argentine film directed by Luis Bayn Herrera and written by Carlos A. Petit and Rodolfo Sciammarella. It stars Blanquita Amaro and Otto Sirgo. Blanquita Amaro Otto Sirgo Tito Lusiardo Juan Lado Mara Esther Gamas Hctor Pal
